Steps:

+ Open Terminal on Raspberry Pi
+ Type sudo nano /etc/opt/AlexaPi/config.yaml
+ Scroll down to the below part 
   pocketsphinx:
    enabled: true
    voice_confirm: true

    phrase: "alexa"
    threshold: 1e-10
    
 + Change phrase: "alexa" to phase: "pixar"
 + Close and save the config.yaml file
 + Type sudo systemctl start AlexaPi.service to restart Pixa
